applicationLogic.statistics
Class AuthorsStatistics

java.lang.Object
  applicationLogic.statistics.AuthorsStatistics

public class AuthorsStatistics
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a container of some conference or journal statistics. The year field is used to store the year for a conference or the volume number for a transaction. For each year / volume this structure stores some statistics on the authors numbers
